            "title": "美銀料中國官方赤字目標或提高至3.8% 經濟增長目標料續定於5%左右",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">外電引述美銀報告，預期中國今年官方經濟增長目標仍定於5%左右，赤字目標則或會升至起碼3.8%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241014_FI_source-ap_China_Economy-3.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20241014_FI_source-ap_China_Economy-3.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">今年中國兩會將於下周召開；美銀指出，從內地3大省份陸續公布的增長目標來看，相信中央對今年經濟增長目標仍會定於5%左右，貨幣政策立場則有望維持寬鬆，未來料將進一步降息及降準，預計全年減息幅度不會超過30點子。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美銀又相信，中央會出台更多財政政策以振興經濟，赤字目標或會由去年的3%，提升到起碼3.8%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14729411-%e7%be%8e%e9%8a%80%e6%96%99%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%ae%98%e6%96%b9%e8%b5%a4%e5%ad%97%e7%9b%ae%e6%a8%99%e6%88%96%e6%8f%90%e9%ab%98%e8%87%b33-8-%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f%e5%a2%9e%e9%95%b7%e7%9b%ae%e6%a8%99",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-ap_ChinaEco-4.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-24 16:35:39",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股午後窄幅   中芯創上市新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數午後窄幅，現跌61點或0.26%，報23416，國指跌18點或0.22%，報8647點，科指跌59點或1.01%，報5799。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：華潤萬象生活官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250224_FI_source-web_01209-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：華潤萬象生活官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250224_FI_source-web_01209-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：華潤萬象生活官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華潤萬象(01109)升8.51%，報31.15元 ; 龍湖(00960)升5.66%，報10.48元 ; 金沙(01928)升5.01%，報18.04元。為表現最佳三藍籌股。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥明康德(02359)挫9.86%，報63.1元 ; 藥明生物(02269)跌8.85%，報23.7元 ; 快手(01024)跌5.14%，報55.4元。為表現最差三藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">晶片股升，華虹(01347)升3.35%，報41.65元 ; 中芯(00981)升1.85%，報55.2元，高見57.6元，為歷史新高。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科指新貴地平線(09660)升6.9%，報8.68元 ; 騰訊音樂(01698)升11.34%，報57.95元。</p>\n</div>",
